snippet.title: Dracula: Reign of Terror (intro)
snippet.description:
Here's the intro for the '97 rts game Dracula: Reign of Terror (or Vlad Tepes Dracula).
The game works well with Win7 (64bit), as long as you mute the ingame sound (the cutscenes are all right, but ingame you can only hear static noises)
